            <title>[WFCORE-526] &quot;patch apply&quot; over a CommandContext bound to existing ModelControllerClient fails</title>
                <link>https://issues.jboss.org/browse/WFCORE-526</link>
                <project id="12315422" key="WFCORE">WildFly Core</project>
